Show HN: hnterminal, terminal browser for Hacker News
text:
Browse HN in terminal CLI, with high degree of flexibility.

`pip install hnterminal`

See readme for detailed usage, or just run `$ hnterminal` and type "help"

Suggestion, feedback and pull requests welcome, next step would be to add login and reply capabilities.

title: Ask HN: I spent 16 credits on DALL-E and it failed to generate intended image
text:
I've registered my account at open.ai recently and spend 16 free credits on DALL-E to generate an image I wanted from the field of macroscopic electrical engineering and biology, with rather detailed queries, and it failed. I used "photo" and "3D render" for style, maybe it imposed some constraints. The thing I want from it isn't rocket science and seems easily doable in Photoshop/Blender. But it failed to generate a single image I wanted.
Is DALL-E really worth it?
